{
  "html": "<h2 id=\"symfony-2\">Symfony 2+</h2>\n\n<p>Install the <code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">sentry/sentry-symfony</code> package:</p>\n\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code><span class=\"nv\">$ </span>composer require sentry/sentry-symfony\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Enable the bundle in <code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">app/AppKernel.php</code>:</p>\n\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code><span class=\"cp\">&lt;?php</span>\n<span class=\"k\">class</span> <span class=\"nc\">AppKernel</span> <span class=\"k\">extends</span> <span class=\"nx\">Kernel</span>\n<span class=\"p\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">public</span> <span class=\"k\">function</span> <span class=\"nf\">registerBundles</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"nv\">$bundles</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"k\">array</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n            <span class=\"c1\">// ...</span>\n\n            <span class=\"k\">new</span> <span class=\"nx\">Sentry\\SentryBundle\\SentryBundle</span><span class=\"p\">(),</span>\n        <span class=\"p\">);</span>\n\n        <span class=\"c1\">// ...</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n    <span class=\"c1\">// ...</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Add your DSN to <code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">app/config/config.yml</code>:</p>\n\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code><span class=\"na\">sentry</span><span class=\"pi\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"na\">dsn</span><span class=\"pi\">:</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"s\">___PUBLIC_DSN___\"</span>\n</code></pre>", 
  "link": "https://docs.sentry.io/clients/php/integrations/symfony2/", 
  "id": "php-symfony2", 
  "name": "Symfony2"
}
